00:00:10.290 --> 00:00:13.889
with a watermelon slice that you can
make

00:00:13.889 --> 00:00:16.910
in just a couple of minutes with nine

00:00:16.910 --> 00:00:20.619
green rubber band and 11 red rubber
bands

